data.description: Fantastic newer home now available in convenient South side location! This great home was built by Pepper Viner Homes in 2010. You will be pleased with this nice floor plan featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 1,222 sf, beautiful tile throughout (except in bedrooms), central a/c, covered patio, and one car garage. Extra tile will be left in the house in case the buyer wants to install the same tile in the bedrooms. This house is very well maintained and it's ready for a new owner. Come view it and don't miss out on one of the best homes in this price range.
